{
  "texts": [
    "Two tools, namely Dextr and ExaCT, focused exclusively on extraction.",
    "The remaining two tools, Iris.ai and RobotReviewer/RobotSearch, had a dual focus on both screening and extraction.",
    "In summary, 19 tools can be used for the screening phase and 4 tools for the extraction phase.",
    "The majority of the tools (19) are web applications, while only 2, namely SWIFT-Review and ASReview, need to be installed locally.",
    "Furthermore, only 4 tools (Colandr, ASReview, FAST2, and RobotReviewer) release their code under an open license."
  ]
}